{"tid":501113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連photo係圖片咁簡單都唔識嘅人應該驅逐出境","createTime":"2017-12-16T13:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T03:40:35.000Z","uid":146924,"like":242,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"19b0db3109cfa09fd194cf832efd9b8bcb557068","tid":501113,"uid":146924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:34:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啲新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成世人不思進取 得過且過<br />\n<br />\n周街都英文指示同標記 <br />\n唔係要你好叻，唔識講都唔緊要<br />\n但menu toilet photo lunch <br />\n咁撚簡單都唔識嘅話 香港真係唔啱你住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔識就學 認個字有幾難<br />\n講緊係你長遠幾十年都想喺度生活<br />\n下下伸手黨問人呢個字係咩 喂埋你食好無！<br />\n你唔煩人地都煩啦<br />\n<br />\n香港放啲蝗狗落嚟已經無移民試 對你無要求<br />\n但做人可唔可以唔好咁不思進取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學多兩個生字 方便日常生活都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死撚咗去啦"},{"pid":"475c759412f4f58743d4c0a5b2d245dedd00728d","tid":501113,"uid":78429,"like":897,"dislike":10,"score":887,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:39:51.000Z","msg":"photo係相<br />\npicture先係圖片<br />\n<br />\n樓主幾時出境?"},{"pid":"49c9f76f46cac045657124f6947a28211ebd98ea","tid":501113,"uid":26156,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:42:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c84b663d6a4fe9585b75208214234aa13ae85649","tid":501113,"uid":15084,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:42:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>photo係相<br />\npicture先係圖片<br />\n<br />\n樓主幾時出境?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03892ceb45033fb17ba415b71e71dc0ac4dffb86",